266
00:17:57,243 --> 00:17:58,493
Trenutak.

267
00:18:08,629 --> 00:18:10,005
Molim?

268
00:18:10,173 --> 00:18:13,508
<i>George. Prošao sam takve situacije.</i>

269
00:18:13,676 --> 00:18:18,513
<i>Volio bih ti dati težak savjet,
