270
00:18:19,098 --> 00:18:20,140
Dobro.

271
00:18:21,225 --> 00:18:23,685
Prihvati tu grozotu.

272
00:18:23,853 --> 00:18:26,646
Odustani od sputavajućih iluzija.
Najteže je prihvatiti

273
00:18:26,814 --> 00:18:30,150
da bez obzira na ishod,

274
00:18:30,318 --> 00:18:36,281
