biti osoba koja si dosad bio.

275
00:18:38,409 --> 00:18:42,204
Dobro, hvala.
Mogu li te poslije nazvati?

276
00:18:42,371 --> 00:18:46,208
Svaki daljnji kontakt
bio bi neprimjeren.

277
00:18:47,043 --> 00:18:49,169
Sretno, George.

278
00:18:55,218 --> 00:18:58,470
