Da, George je.

279
00:18:58,638 --> 00:19:01,139
Moram razgovarati s njim.

280
00:19:01,516 --> 00:19:04,559
Da, javite mu što prije.

281
00:19:04,727 --> 00:19:06,102
Hvala.

282
00:19:08,439 --> 00:19:12,859
Zdravo, George ovdje. Ostavio sam
vam četiri hitne poruke.

283
00:19:13,027 --> 00:19:16,696
Znate da umanjujem važnost,
ne shvaćam zašto se ne javljate.

284
00:19:17,573 --> 00:19:18,949
Hvala.

285
00:19:19,450 --> 00:19:21,868
Pa, reci mi.
Sigurno imaš neko mišljenje.

286
00:19:22,370 --> 00:19:24,454
Imam.

287
00:19:24,622 --> 00:19:26,581
No ne ponosim se njime.

288
00:19:27,208 --> 00:19:29,292
Ja i moje analiziranje.

289
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:33,213
Razmišljala sam o svom poslu.

290
00:19:33,381 --> 00:19:34,881
Objasnit ću ti.

291
00:19:43,182 --> 00:19:46,643
Ovo činim zbog nas, kunem se.

292
00:19:50,064 --> 00:19:52,941
Ne odgovaramo si
u ovom razdoblju tvog života.

293
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:56,403
Ja imam taj rok,
a tebe istražuju.

294
00:19:56,571 --> 00:19:59,781
Ne želim da naša veza
postane hrana za topove

295
00:19:59,949 --> 00:20:02,784
za tu sablast
u tvom poslovnom životu.

296
00:20:03,327 --> 00:20:06,079
Bit ću uz tebe na kraju.

297
00:20:06,247 --> 00:20:07,581
Na to možeš računati.

298
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:12,419
Želiš da se raziđemo
dok ne riješim problem?

299
00:20:12,587 --> 00:20:13,837
Molim te, voljela bih...

300
00:20:14,005 --> 00:20:18,091
Prekidaš sa mnom? Prekidaš?

301
00:20:18,259 --> 00:20:20,802
Samo uzimam stanku!

302
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:24,639
Da ne trošimo dragocjenu
energiju na gluposti.

303
00:21:22,823 --> 00:21:24,449
Ne.

304
00:21:24,617 --> 00:21:26,868
Ne. Ne.

305
00:21:28,162 --> 00:21:30,038
Ni to. Ne bih, hvala.

306
00:21:34,710 --> 00:21:36,419
<i>Večeras sam</i>

307
00:21:37,004 --> 00:21:40,924
<i>Romantično raspoložen, da</i>

308
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:43,885
<i>Istuširajmo se</i>

309
00:21:45,346 --> 00:21:47,305
<i>Istuširajmo se zajedno</i>

310
00:21:48,974 --> 00:21:51,559
<i>Ja ću oprati tvoje tijelo</i>

311
00:21:51,727 --> 00:21:54,437
<i>A ti operi moje</i>

312
00:21:56,399 --> 00:22:01,361
<i>Namaži me
vrućim uljem, draga</i>

313
00:22:01,529 --> 00:22:02,529
<i>Da</i>

314
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:11,413
Molim? Molim?

315
00:22:12,707 --> 00:22:13,748
<i>Molim?</i>

316
00:22:13,916 --> 00:22:15,583
<i>-Bok, šefe.
-Bok!</i>

317
00:22:15,751 --> 00:22:17,752
<i>-Kako si? Nije prekasno...
-Nije.</i>

318
00:22:18,671 --> 00:22:20,797
U redu je. Pričekaj trenutak.

319
00:22:21,090 --> 00:22:22,090
Dobro.

320
00:22:27,346 --> 00:22:30,724
Hvala ti što si nazvala.

321
00:22:31,434 --> 00:22:34,477
Ne mogu spavati. Ne znam
što me jutros obuzelo.

322
00:22:34,645 --> 00:22:37,105
Nikad nikoga nisam udarila.

323
00:22:37,273 --> 00:22:39,274
Zapravo znam. Trudna sam.

324
00:22:39,775 --> 00:22:41,651
Trudna si!

325
00:22:42,361 --> 00:22:45,780
Da, tajna se doznala.

326
00:22:46,532 --> 00:22:48,074
<i>Trudna si!</i>

327
00:22:48,367 --> 00:22:49,951
Sumnjao sam u to.

328
00:22:57,960 --> 00:23:00,420
