00:30:03,218 --> 00:30:04,719
Samo recite: ''Dobro, Lisa.''

421
00:30:05,053 --> 00:30:06,929
Dobro, Lisa.

422
00:30:07,723 --> 00:30:09,098
Bože.

423
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:14,854
Moram ići. Čeka me.

424
00:30:15,022 --> 00:30:16,981
-Volim vas!
-Volimo te!

