426
00:30:19,443 --> 00:30:21,068
Bravo, Lise.

427
00:30:33,582 --> 00:30:35,249
-Zdravo.
-Ime, molim.

428
00:30:35,417 --> 00:30:36,918
Nalazim se s Georgeom...

429
00:30:37,085 --> 00:30:40,671
