430
00:30:46,511 --> 00:30:49,055
Je li ono on?

431
00:30:50,474 --> 00:30:52,225
Kladim se da jest.

432
00:30:52,768 --> 00:30:55,061
Takav mi je dan.

433
00:30:56,230 --> 00:30:58,940
Ne morate me otpratiti.
Hvala vam svejedno.

434
00:31:05,781 --> 00:31:07,281
George?

435
00:31:08,325 --> 00:31:09,784
Jesi li ti George?

436
00:31:10,786 --> 00:31:12,495
Ja sam Lisa.

437
00:31:12,663 --> 00:31:15,164
-Drago mi je što si mi se pridružila.
